    "id": "cloche-9gc",
    "title": "Fix step-level log history display in web UI and CLI",
    "description": "Step-level log output (e.g. 'implement', 'test') no longer shows up when expanding a step in the web UI. The main log stream works correctly, but we need to capture and display the full history per step as well. When expanding a step like 'implement', show all logs captured to date for that step, then continue updating with new streaming lines. Same for the CLI — 'cloche logs --step \u003cname\u003e' should show historical logs to date, then stream updates as they arrive.",
